Projectile hook (ctor):
args[0] = projPtr (pointer)    - the projectile instance
args[1] = ownerPtr (pointer)   - the character who shot it
args[2] = dataPtr (pointer)    - projectile data/config

Projectile tracking State.projectiles:
{
    id:       int    - global ID from projPtr
    x:        float  - spawn X
    y:        float  - spawn Y
    speed:    float  - from LogicProjectileData_getSpeed(dataPtr)
    radius:   float  - from LogicProjectileData_getRadius(dataPtr)
    angle:    float  - from LogicProjectileClient_getAngle(projPtr)
    lastSeen: int    - Date.now() timestamp
    own:      bool   - ownerPtr equals State.ownCharPtr
}
